data.description: Welcome to your ideal starter home! This beautifully renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence is move-in ready, situated on a generous lot of almost an acre. A welcoming, elongated driveway provides ample space for family and friends, setting the stage for the wonderful features awaiting you inside.    Step into the heart of the home—the kitchen features quartz countertops, a fresh backsplash, and pristine white cabinets, complemented by stainless steel appliances and a cozy breakfast area. The fully renovated bathrooms boast new showers, tubs, vanities, faucets, and plumbing fixtures, ensuring both style and functionality.    Enjoy worry-free living with new flooring, newer windows, lighting, and HVAC. The back deck offers a perfect spot for summer BBQs, while the spacious backyard provides ample room for kids and pets to play.    Noteworthy is the front-yard placement of the septic field, creating an opportunity to maximize the backyard space for potential additions like a pool or guest house.    Conveniently located near schools, restaurants, and shopping, this home is the perfect introduction to comfortable and stylish living. The seller sweetens the deal by offering a home warranty for added peace of mind. Don't miss out on the chance to make this charming starter home your own. Move in, unpack, and start creating memories!
